            <thetext>When a combobox is in a qx.ui.window.Window and the window gets closed programmatically while the popuplist is visible, the popuplist stays visible while the window gets closed.

A patch against rev. 4478 is attached which adds a &quot;beforedisappear&quot; event to the combobox which closes the popuplist.</thetext>
